歌曲以[[升C小調|升C小調]]創作，每分鐘80拍，時長3分5秒<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://musicstax.com/track/the-plan/551xyaSJsg8hILXFq9JdST |title=Key and BPM of The Plan by Travis Scott |website=musicstax.com |language=en-US |accessdate=2020-09-15 |archivedate=2020-09-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915155601/https://musicstax.com/track/the-plan/551xyaSJsg8hILXFq9JdST |deadurl=no }}</ref>，有著斯科特招牌的深沉[[自动调谐|自动调谐]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.abc.net.au/triplej/news/musicnews/listen-travis-scott-the-plan-tenet-movie-song-christopher-nolan/12584016 |title=Listen to Travis Scott's new Tenet single 'The Plan' |work=[[澳大利亚广播公司|ABC]] |date=2020-08-23 |accessdate=2020-09-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916052240/https://www.abc.net.au/triplej/news/musicnews/listen-travis-scott-the-plan-tenet-movie-song-christopher-nolan/12584016 |archivedate=2020-09-16 }}</ref>。〈{{lang|en|The Plan}}〉的作詞作曲由斯科特、[[魯德溫·葛瑞森|魯德溫·葛瑞森]]、{{le|埃博妮·奧順林德|WondaGurl}}共同完成<ref name="credits" />，這也是斯科特首次為電影製作歌曲<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/9436582/travis-scott-tenet-song-details |title=Travis Scott Is Ready to Melt Your Brain With His 'Tenet' Theme Song: Here's When You Can Hear It |first=Gil |last=Kaufman |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=2020-08-21 |accessdate=2020-08-29 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829234458/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/9436582/travis-scott-tenet-song-details |archivedate=2020-08-29 }}</ref>。〈{{lang|en|The Plan}}〉從震撼的低音循環開始，這也是整個歌曲的基調，隨著[[合唱|合唱]]的段落到來，[[中斷|中斷]]了充滿不詳氣氛的曲調。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]》認為，斯科特在歌曲中的快節奏演唱讓人聯想到[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]在《[[心碎節拍|心碎節拍]]》專輯的表現<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/music/news/travis-scott-tenet-the-plan-christopher-nolan-1234744625/ |title=Travis Scott Releases New Song ‘The Plan’ From Christopher Nolan’s ‘Tenet’ |first=Ellise |last=Shafer |date=2020-08-22 |accessdate=2020-09-16 |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916055107/https://variety.com/2020/music/news/travis-scott-tenet-the-plan-christopher-nolan-1234744625/ |archivedate=2020-09-16 }}</ref>。和電影《TENET天能》相同，歌曲以時間順行與逆行的概念構成<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://screenrant.com/tenet-movie-travis-scott-plan-song-reveals/ |title=Tenet: What Travis Scott's "The Plan" Reveals About Nolan's Movie |first=Craig |last=Elvy |date=2020-08-22 |accessdate=2020-09-16 |work=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916051333/https://screenrant.com/tenet-movie-travis-scott-plan-song-reveals/ |archivedate=2020-09-16 }}</ref>。

在電影製作期間，葛瑞森看完《TENET天能》後覺得結尾應該要有能傳達（觀眾）剛剛歷險過程的媒介，此時他首先想到的是特拉维斯·斯科特。葛瑞森表示的歌聲與電影概念吻合，根據他的經驗這正是诺兰想要的<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/travis-scott-the-plan-song-tenet-soundtrack-1047792/ |title=Travis Scott Drops New Song ‘The Plan’ From ‘Tenet’ Soundtrack |first1=Althea |last1=Legaspi |first2=Daniel |last2=Kreps |date=2020-08-22 |accessdate=2020-09-15 |work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915191503/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/travis-scott-the-plan-song-tenet-soundtrack-1047792/ |archivedate=2020-09-15 }}</ref>。導演[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]接受《[[GQ|GQ]]》採訪時稱〈{{lang|en|The Plan}}〉是電影的「最後一塊拼圖」，歌曲和電影相得益彰，斯科特在音樂上的觀點，加上我跟葛瑞森建立起的敘事結構，立即造就了具洞察力且意義深遠的創作<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gq.com/story/travis-scott-september-2020-cover-profile |title=How Travis Scott Defied the Rules of Celebrity to Become King of the Youth |first=Gerrick |last=D. Kennedy |date=2020-08-18 |accessdate=2020-09-15 |work=[[GQ|GQ]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904144913/https://www.gq.com/story/travis-scott-september-2020-cover-profile |archivedate=2020-09-04 }}</ref>。

==發行==
2020年8月18日，[[特拉维斯·斯科特|特拉维斯·斯科特]]在自己的社群網站公布了〈{{lang|en|The Plan}}〉的單曲封面<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rap-up.com/2020/08/19/travis-scott-announces-tenet-single-the-plan/amp/ |title=Travis Scott Announces ‘Tenet’ Single ‘The Plan’ |date=2020-08-19 |accessdate=2020-09-16 |work={{le|Rap-Up}} |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916045326/https://www.rap-up.com/2020/08/19/travis-scott-announces-tenet-single-the-plan/amp/ |archivedate=2020-09-16 }}</ref>，8月21日正式發行，並於《{{le|NBA on TNT}}》首次公開亮相<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.vulture.com/2020/08/travis-scott-drops-new-song-the-plan-from-tenet-soundtrack.html |title=Listen to Travis Scott’s New Song ‘The Plan’ From Christoper Nolan’s Tenet Soundtrack |first=Halle |last=Kiefer |date=2020-08-22 |accessdate=2020-09-15 |work={{le|Vulture.com}} |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915180431/https://www.vulture.com/2020/08/travis-scott-drops-new-song-the-plan-from-tenet-soundtrack.html |archivedate=2020-09-15 }}</ref>。為配合電影宣傳，斯科特在自己的商店推出造型[[T恤|T恤]]，限時24小時販售<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://respect-mag.com/2020/08/travis-scott-releases-new-single-the-plan-for-tenet-with-limited-edition-cactus-jack-for-tenet-t-shirt-available-for-24-hours/ |title=Travis Scott Releases New Single “The Plan” For ‘Tenet’ With Limited Edition Cactus Jack For ‘Tenet’ T-Shirt Available For 24 Hours |first=Ayana |last=Rashed |date=2020-08-22 |accessdate=2020-09-15 |work={{le|Respect (雜誌)|Respect (magazine)|Respect}} |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915175535/https://respect-mag.com/2020/08/travis-scott-releases-new-single-the-plan-for-tenet-with-limited-edition-cactus-jack-for-tenet-t-shirt-available-for-24-hours/ |archivedate=2020-09-15 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hypebeast.cn/2020/8/travis-scott-cactus-jack-for-tenet-t-shirt-release |title=Travis Scott 推出科幻电影《信条 Tenet》全新别注 T-Shirt |first=Leo |last=Huang |date=2020-08-22 |accessdate=2020-09-15 |work=HYPEBEAST |language=zh-hans |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915175428/https://hypebeast.cn/2020/8/travis-scott-cactus-jack-for-tenet-t-shirt-release |archivedate=2020-09-15 }}</ref>。

==評價==
[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork]]的編輯布蘭登·卡倫德（Brandon Callender）表示〈{{lang|en|The Plan}}〉是首適合在畫面漸漸變暗要開始進入工作人員清單時演奏的歌曲類型，觀眾甚至不會注意到他音樂何時開始<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/tracks/travis-scott-the-plan/ |title=Travis Scott “The Plan” |first=Brandon |last=Callender |date=2020-08-24 |accessdate=2020-09-16 |work=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork]] |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916053551/https://pitchfork.com/reviews/tracks/travis-scott-the-plan/ |archivedate=2020-09-16 }}</ref>。《The Edge》的編輯西奧·史密斯（Theo Smith）給予歌曲4星（滿分5星），認為歌曲在三分鐘內，斯科特憑藉著沉重的低音、震撼的合成器、失真的背景吉他加上他的特色自动调谐與怪異的人聲，營造出了情緒不穩的電影氛圍，非常契合電影的主題<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theedgesusu.co.uk/records/singles/2020/08/25/review-travis-scott-the-plan-a-strange-match-that-fits-into-a-larger-picture/ |title=Review: Travis Scott – The Plan; A Strange Match That Fits into a Larger Picture |first=Theo |last=Smith |date=2020-08-25 |accessdate=2020-09-16 |work=The Edge |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916052928/https://www.theedgesusu.co.uk/records/singles/2020/08/25/review-travis-scott-the-plan-a-strange-match-that-fits-into-a-larger-picture/ |archivedate=2020-09-16 }}</ref>。

